    <item>
      <title>特朗普提供 1 亿美元债券以上诉纽约欺诈判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/trump-offering-100-million-bond-to-appeal-ny-fraud-verdict</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 提出提供 1 亿美元的保证金，以便他能够对纽约民事欺诈案中针对他的 4.54 亿美元的判决提出质疑，称否则他可能不得不出售房产来筹集现金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/trump-offering-100-million-bond-to-appeal-ny-fraud-verdict</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 19:30:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普因克林顿诉讼失败而被罚款 937,989 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/trump-revives-fight-over-937-989-fine-in-failed-clinton-suit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，佛罗里达州一名联邦法官因对希拉里·克林顿提出“无意义的”指控而对他处以 937,989 美元的罚款，唐纳德·特朗普正在努力扭转这一局面。这位前总统为应对一系列代价高昂的法庭损失而做出的又一次努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/trump-revives-fight-over-937-989-fine-in-failed-clinton-suit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 18:17:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉无视美国斡旋的协议，迫使拜登重新实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/venezuela-flouts-us-brokered-deal-pressing-biden-to-reimpose-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉为今年的选举设定了新的条件，无视美国斡旋的协议，并可能引发华盛顿更严厉的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/venezuela-flouts-us-brokered-deal-pressing-biden-to-reimpose-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 18:14:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和欧洲在动用 2800 亿美元俄罗斯资产问题上存在分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/us-and-europe-at-odds-on-tapping-280-billion-of-russian-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国及其欧洲盟友表示，他们决心利用冻结的俄罗斯资产以某种方式帮助乌克兰。本周在巴西，他们正在讨论在不陷入法律或财务风险的情况下实现这一目标的最佳方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/us-and-europe-at-odds-on-tapping-280-billion-of-russian-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 18:06:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党称下一届英国政府面临战后最糟糕的继承</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/labour-says-next-uk-government-faces-worst-inheritance-since-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[影子财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯表示，英国反对党工党如果赢得下次选举，将面临二战以来最糟糕的经济遗产，因为执政的保守党已经花费了太多钱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/labour-says-next-uk-government-faces-worst-inheritance-since-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 17:35:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党拥抱特朗普，麦康奈尔将放弃领导职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/mcconnell-to-step-down-as-senate-republican-leader-post-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党人米奇·麦康奈尔 (Mitch McConnell) 将在 11 月大选后辞去参议院党魁一职，从而引发一场激烈的继任之争，而这场斗争将由对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的忠诚推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/mcconnell-to-step-down-as-senate-republican-leader-post-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 17:28:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国最高法院在枪支冲突中质疑撞车禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/bump-stock-ban-questioned-by-us-supreme-court-in-gun-clash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院考虑对枪支法规进行新的打击，因为法官们对联邦禁止撞枪托的禁令提出质疑，撞枪托是一种能让半自动步枪以与机枪相当的速度射击的附件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/bump-stock-ban-questioned-by-us-supreme-court-in-gun-clash</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 17:02:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在年度体检后宣称自己的健康状况“很好”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/biden-81-headed-for-annual-physical-at-walter-reed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登周三在选举季接受了年度体检，选民对他的年龄和是否适合连任第二个任期表示担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/biden-81-headed-for-annual-physical-at-walter-reed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:08:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加州大学伯克利分校因反以色列抗议者在活动中强制疏散而感到不安</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/uc-berkeley-condemns-anti-israel-protesters-who-forced-evacuation-at-event</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州大学伯克利分校领导层谴责了那些在抗议者包围并闯入一栋大楼并导致大楼疏散后强行取消以色列演讲者活动的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/uc-berkeley-condemns-anti-israel-protesters-who-forced-evacuation-at-event</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:47:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩尔多瓦叛乱地区向普京求助，因为其影响力下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/moldova-s-breakaway-region-appeals-for-help-from-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩尔多瓦的分离地区德涅斯特河左岸呼吁莫斯科在与中央政府的对峙中提供援助，因为亲欧洲的总统马亚·桑杜政府试图重申对这片俄语飞地的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/moldova-s-breakaway-region-appeals-for-help-from-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:12:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
